data.value:
Binding privileged ports (<1024) on Linux requires CAP_NET_BIND_SERVICE or root.

Option 1 - Grant capability to the executable (recommended for desktop apps):
  sudo setcap 'cap_net_bind_service=+ep' {0}

Option 2 - Run the host as root (not recommended):
  sudo {0}

Option 3 - Use an unprivileged port (>=1024), e.g. {1}
